quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  53,0,Allah ke naam se jo Rehman o Raheem hai
  53,1,qaisam hai tarre ki jabkay woh ghuroob howa
  53,2,tumhara Rafeeq nah bhatka hai nah b_hka hai
  53,3,woh apni khwahish nafs se nahi boltaa
  53,4,yeh to aik wahi hai jo uss par nazil ki jati hai
  53,5,ussay zabardast qowat walay ne taleem di hai
  53,6,jo bara sahib hikmat hai
  53,7,woh samnay aa khara howa jabkay woh balai ufaq par tha
  53,8,phir qareeb aaya aur oopar muallaq ho gaya
  53,9,yahan taq ke do kamaanon ke barabar ya is se kuch kam faasla reh gaya
  53,10,tab uss ne Allah ke bande ko wahi pohanchai jo wahi bhi ussay p_hnchani thi
  53,11,"nazar ne jo kuch dekha, dil ne uss mein jhoot nah milaya"
  53,12,ab kya tum uss cheez par uss se jhagarte ho jisay woh aankhon se daikhta hai ?
  53,13,aur aik martaba phir uss ne
  53,14,sidra tul muntah ke paas uss ko dekha
  53,15,jahan paas hi jannat ul mawa hai
  53,16,uss waqt sidra par chhaa raha tha jo kuch ke chhaa raha tha
  53,17,nigah nah chndyainah hadd se mutajawajz hui
  53,18,aur is ne apne rab ki barri barri nishanain dekhen
  53,19,"ab zara batao, tum ne kabhi iss laat, aur iss uzza"
  53,20,aur teesri aik aur devi menat ki haqeeqat par kuch ghhor bhi kya ?
  53,21,kya betay tumahray liye hain aur betiyan khuda ke liye ?
  53,22,yeh to barri dhandli ki taqseem hui !
  53,23,darasal yeh kuch nahi hain magar bas chand naam jo tum ne aur tumahray baap dada ne rakh liye hain Allah ne inn ke liye koi sanad nazil nahi ki haqeeqat yeh hai ke log mehez vahm o gumaan ki pairwi kar rahay hain aur khwahisaat nafs ke mureed banay hue hain halaank unn ke rab ki taraf se unn ke paas hadaayat aa chuki hai
  53,24,kya ensaan jo kuch chahay is ke liye wahi haq hai
  53,25,duniya aur akhirat ka maalik to Allah hi hai
  53,26,"asmano mein kitney hi farishtay mojood hain, unn ki Shafaat kuch bhi kaam nahi aa sakti jab taq ke Allah kisi aisay shakhs ke haq mein uss ki ijazat nah day jis ke liye woh koi arzdasht sunna chahay aur is ko pasand kere"
  53,27,magar jo log akhirat ko nahi mantay woh firshton ko deviyon ke naamon se mosoom karte hain
  53,28,"halaank is maamla ka koi ilm inhen haasil nahi hai, woh mehez gumaan ki pairwi kar rahay hain, aur gumaan haq ki jagah kuch bhi kaam nahi day sakta"
  53,29,"pas ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, jo shakhs hamaray zikar se mun pherte hai, aur duniya ki zindagi ke siwa jisay kuch matloob nahi hai, ussay is ke haal par chore do"
  53,30,"inn logon ka mubalagh ilm bas yahi kuch hai, yeh baat tera rab hi ziyada jaanta hai ke uss ke rastay se kon bhatak gaya hai aur kon seedhay rastay par hai"
  53,31,aur zameen aur asmano ki har cheez ka maalik Allah hi hai taakay Allah buraiee karne walon ko un ke amal ka badla day aur unn logon ko achi jaza se nawaze jinhon ne naik rawayya ikhtiyar kya hai
  53,32,"jo barray barray gunaaho aur khulay khulay qabeeh af-aal se parhaiz karte hain, ila yeh ke kuch qasoor unn se sarzad ho jaye bilashuba tairay rab ka daman mughfirat bohat wasee hai woh tumhen uss waqt se khoob jaanta hai jab uss ne zameen se tumhe peda kya aur jab tum apni maaon ke piton mein abhi janeen hi thay pas apne nafs ki paki ke daaway nah karo, wohi behtar jaanta hai ke waqai mut-taqi kon hai"
  53,33,"phir ae NabiSallallahu Alaihi Wasallam, tum ne uss shakhs ko bhi dekha jo raah khuda se phir gaya"
  53,34,aur thora sa day kar ruk gaya
  53,35,kya is ke paas ghaib ka ilm hai ke woh haqeeqat ko dekh raha hai ?
  53,36,kya ussay unn baton ki koi khabar nahi pohanchi jo moose ke saheefon
  53,37,aur uss ibrahim ke saheefon mein bayan hui hain jis ne wafa ka haq ada kar diya ?
  53,38,""" yeh ke koi boojh uthany wala dosray ka boojh nahi uthaye ga"
  53,39,aur yeh ke ensaan ke liye kuch nahi hai magar woh jis ki uss ne sae ki hai
  53,40,aur yeh ke is ki sae anqareeb dekhi jaye gi
  53,41,aur is ki poori jaza usay di jaye gi
  53,42,aur yeh ke aakhir-kaar pohanchna tairay rab hi ke paas hai
  53,43,aur yeh ke usi ne hansaya aur usi ne rulaya
  53,44,aur yeh ke usi ne mout di aur usi ne zindagi bakhsh
  53,45,aur yeh ke usi ne nar aur madah ka jora peda kya
  53,46,aik boond se jab woh tapkai jati hai
  53,47,aur yeh ke doosri zindagi bakhshna bhi usi ke zimma hai
  53,48,aur yeh ke usi ne ghanni kya aur jaidaad bakhsh
  53,49,aur yeh ke wohi sheri ka rab hai
  53,50,aur yeh ke usi ne Aad-e- Owlaa ko halaak kya
  53,51,aur samood ko aisa mitaya ke un mein se kisi ko baqi nah chorra
  53,52,aur unn se pehlay qoum Nooh ko tabah kya kyunkay woh thay hi sakht zalim o sarkash log
  53,53,aur ondhee girnay wali bustiyon ko utha phenka
  53,54,phir chhaa diya unn par woh kuch jo ( tum jantay hi ho ke ) kya chhaa diya
  53,55,"pas ae mukhatib, apne rab ki kin kin nematon mein to shak kere ga? """
  53,56,yeh aik tanbeeh hai pehlay aayi hui tnbihat mein se
  53,57,anay wali gharri qareeb aa lagi hai
  53,58,Allah ke siwa koi uss ko hata ne wala nahi
  53,59,ab kya yahi woh baatein hain jin par tum izhaar taajjub karte ho ?
  53,60,hanstay ho aur rotay nahi ho ?
  53,61,aur ga baja kar inhen talte ho ?
  53,62,jhuk jao Allah ke agay aur bandagi baja lao
